::Prowl/Kluster::

Prowl frowns, thinking over what Arcangel said.

"We fix the Ark, and then we do something else," he says to Arcangel, 
begining his decent toward the Ark when a transmission stops him.

"Prowl," Kluster's voice says over the comm-link, "Lunarpine commed in. He 
was babbling about something about you contacting him and that you're an owl."

Prowl frowns. "I'll contact him," he says.

"Lunarpine," he says into his comm-link, "This is Prowl, you wanted to talk 
to me?"
